.TH "xdr_stream_decode_opaque" 9 "xdr_stream_decode_opaque" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xdr_stream_decode_opaque \- Decode variable length opaque
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "ssize_t" xdr_stream_decode_opaque
.BI "(struct xdr_stream *xdr "  ","
.BI "void *ptr "  ","
.BI "size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "xdr" 12
pointer to xdr_stream
.IP "ptr" 12
location to store opaque data
.IP "size" 12
size of storage buffer \fIptr\fP
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Return values:
On success, returns size of object stored in *\fIptr\fP
-EBADMSG on XDR buffer overflow
-EMSGSIZE on overflow of storage buffer \fIptr\fP
